               <head>Letters of Muhmud Gavan</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Manāẓir al-inshā’ by Maḥmūd Gāwān̲, 1411?-1481</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100074 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85104368 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85129379" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_484-item1">
